The logical steps to breaking down your monolith according to Frye are:

Identify logical components.

Flatten and refactor components.

Identify component dependencies.

Identify component groups.

Create an API for a remote user interface.

Migrate component groups to macroservices:

Move component groups to separate projects.

Make separate deployments.

Migrate macroservices to microservices.

Repeat steps 6â€“7 until complete.